{"tid":2350274,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"聶德權：料2月起5類地點為市民接種　有知情下選擇","createTime":"2021-01-02T07:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T10:02:10.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b51c35739088c91aa4135463b7062f02b00cd847","tid":2350274,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210102/422061696203362304398127.jpeg/A_VGErwttOB2ZXL-0i_WBtwAiJj80-QxPq06bT6tOm0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210102%2F422061696203362304398127.jpeg%2FA_VGErwttOB2ZXL-0i_WBtwAiJj80-QxPq06bT6tOm0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e844760d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新冠肺炎疫情嚴峻，港府已購入中國科興、德國BioNTech / 復星疫苗及英國阿斯利康 / 牛津疫苗。首批為科興疫苗，原訂本月抵港及接種，但有專家稱因臨床數據未公布而推遲。公務員事務局局長聶德權今（2日）在社交網站發文透露，估計可在2月起為市民接種，屆時社區疫苗接種中心、公營醫院、安老院舍、私家醫院和診所都會是接種地點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210102/421995184453062656657804.jpeg/lFOFvXupifivFemzZZ6ts6lfayPeeASazICATsyAgE4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210102%2F421995184453062656657804.jpeg%2FlFOFvXupifivFemzZZ6ts6lfayPeeASazICATsyAgE4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=887dfb0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聶德權指，估計可以在2月開始為市民接種，屆時社區疫苗接種中心、公營醫院、安老院舍、私家醫院和診所均是接種地點。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n▼科興、BioNTECH復星、阿斯利康疫苗保護率副作用▼<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201227/419874127407484928764801.jpeg/RZVwg0yyT9ffx1iu1EFp1vnTQuJ6JaYPcAhORXAITkU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201227%2F419874127407484928764801.jpeg%2FRZVwg0yyT9ffx1iu1EFp1vnTQuJ6JaYPcAhORXAITkU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6126d7c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201227/419873312257085440619735.jpeg/7JdSjxvTmAM5XAtS4cQjET6vs4wsLeCaCcTnAwnE5wM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201227%2F419873312257085440619735.jpeg%2F7JdSjxvTmAM5XAtS4cQjET6vs4wsLeCaCcTnAwnE5wM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=78bbc5fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201227/419873314455031808056731.jpeg/rUH4oXaTO36pJm83YahtNeDuUIVgi2GL6uCvtergr7U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201227%2F419873314455031808056731.jpeg%2FrUH4oXaTO36pJm83YahtNeDuUIVgi2GL6uCvtergr7U%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ba98d79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201227/419873316950773760947125.jpeg/8D085vEpQfCTfZu5tTE_0XWmtMSu_lKzx491dcePdXU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201227%2F419873316950773760947125.jpeg%2F8D085vEpQfCTfZu5tTE_0XWmtMSu_lKzx491dcePdXU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=844766f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201227/419873319312297984538691.jpeg/TVU17kuLpc6j83644FX13D1FE9iaVVw6h7r9woe6_cI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201227%2F419873319312297984538691.jpeg%2FTVU17kuLpc6j83644FX13D1FE9iaVVw6h7r9woe6_cI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=337b0991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201227/419873321808039936621534.jpeg/EpsJqrR-0fXUGpd_CpHDvWFhXajFAIPZlxRSJ5cUUic?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201227%2F419873321808039936621534.jpeg%2FEpsJqrR-0fXUGpd_CpHDvWFhXajFAIPZlxRSJ5cUUic%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7f9f4ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201227/419873324299587584874230.jpeg/kH3KEmBqIck4SSu7ZKItudwB6FR9DUSPnqlFNp6pRTY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201227%2F419873324299587584874230.jpeg%2FkH3KEmBqIck4SSu7ZKItudwB6FR9DUSPnqlFNp6pRTY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c4445d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201227/419873326774358016351806.jpeg/UHLZdcudYbZK5sAW1z_v_dB1VQV39Kf8XAIsE1wCLBM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201227%2F419873326774358016351806.jpeg%2FUHLZdcudYbZK5sAW1z_v_dB1VQV39Kf8XAIsE1wCLBM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=35724ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聶德權今午在Facebook專頁發文指，疫苗接種的專責工作小組本周二（12月29日）舉行了首次跨部門會議，會上多位局長、部門首長、醫療專家成員商討了疫苗接種選址、長者的接種安排、優先群組的設定、醫學監察等範疇，有助制訂疫苗接種方案及執行，強調只要市民願意，所有香港市民都能在安全、穩妥、有序地免費接種疫苗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210102/422055717092986880896530.jpeg/Fj1o9czyJjJqq9vGBK5owSd5AGEuJfY6gnCEs4JwhLM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210102%2F422055717092986880896530.jpeg%2FFj1o9czyJjJqq9vGBK5owSd5AGEuJfY6gnCEs4JwhLM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b97cac0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聶德權今午在Facebook發文指，疫苗接種的專責工作小組本周二（12月29日）舉行了首次跨部門會議。（聶德權fb圖片）<br />\n<br />\n他續指，目標是政府各部門在本月底完成籌備工作，為疫苗抵港做好準備。而按疫苗到港的時間初步推算，估計可以在2月開始為市民接種，屆時社區疫苗接種中心、公營醫院、安老院舍、私家醫院和診所均是接種地點。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>在知情的情況下作出選擇　接種疫苗</strong><br />\n<br />\n對於外界質疑疫苗成效等，聶德權稱，港府接下來會做好有關的解說及公眾教育工作，讓市民有科學性的認識，在知情的情況下作出選擇，接種疫苗，以達到保護自己和防疫的目的。<br />\n<br />\n▼接種疫苗　專家解答九大疑問▼<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201224/418896261534453760532804.jpeg/UJ0HiI_96jsFBxm9sXrdCVdkwJpqGYo5hzb9B4c2_Qc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201224%2F418896261534453760532804.jpeg%2FUJ0HiI_96jsFBxm9sXrdCVdkwJpqGYo5hzb9B4c2_Qc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=30a3ece8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201224/418896264244105216652783.jpeg/qafj_S0eWwqAgOeZ5GOyMVwDM_wlk9ySLXQ2ty10Nrc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201224%2F418896264244105216652783.jpeg%2Fqafj_S0eWwqAgOeZ5GOyMVwDM_wlk9ySLXQ2ty10Nrc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=65ef7d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201224/418896266781790208657024.jpeg/IBZKvSor_aczOxRIlgj9TTcPNGl5uygCkizcn5Is3J8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201224%2F418896266781790208657024.jpeg%2FIBZKvSor_aczOxRIlgj9TTcPNGl5uygCkizcn5Is3J8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=45709bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201224/418896270053478400017923.jpeg/xQxUe2ov85InlJEImA-PGLqD_ZkOnbR_LAggWywIIFs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201224%2F418896270053478400017923.jpeg%2FxQxUe2ov85InlJEImA-PGLqD_ZkOnbR_LAggWywIIFs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=13599330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201224/418896272549220352765342.jpeg/AdQv4NuDpJdS4xwvcBa2gu0dIibGpQwYGO095BjtPeQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201224%2F418896272549220352765342.jpeg%2FAdQv4NuDpJdS4xwvcBa2gu0dIibGpQwYGO095BjtPeQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b5135dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201224/418896275137236992840296.jpeg/eRNZxMiHpRhUE_9pUPD14TfDAtEqbT7EpCZIWqQmSFo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201224%2F418896275137236992840296.jpeg%2FeRNZxMiHpRhUE_9pUPD14TfDAtEqbT7EpCZIWqQmSFo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8b6f1bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201224/418896277922385920360184.jpeg/T5gf2Y1JnlmntCdD2BZF9DZPY_ky2sbQgqPfjYKj340?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201224%2F418896277922385920360184.jpeg%2FT5gf2Y1JnlmntCdD2BZF9DZPY_ky2sbQgqPfjYKj340%3Fv%3Dw192